            <title><![CDATA[【图集】上海浦东机场连夜进行核酸检测]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay"> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202011/20201123/20201123_m_pu_dong_ji_chang_-1.jpg?itok=B1Jl5oD0" alt data-caption="上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。（上海发布微信号）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202011/20201123/20201123_m_pu_dong_ji_chang_-1.jpg?itok=B1Jl5oD0" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。（上海发布微信号）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202011/20201123/20201123_m_pu_dong_ji_chang_-3.jpg?itok=lX-8fIZI" alt data-caption="上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。（上海发布微信号）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202011/20201123/20201123_m_pu_dong_ji_chang_-3.jpg?itok=lX-8fIZI" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。（上海发布微信号）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202011/20201123/20201123_m_pu_dong_ji_chang_-2.jpg?itok=4oxYjlP5" alt data-caption="上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。（上海发布微信号）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202011/20201123/20201123_m_pu_dong_ji_chang_-2.jpg?itok=4oxYjlP5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。（上海发布微信号）</p></figcaption></div><div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div></div>

<p> </p>

<p>上海冠病疫情出现局部反弹，与浦东国际机场关联的冠病确诊病例已增至七起，病毒经国际物流输入的风险引发重视。</p>

<p>综合澎湃新闻、“上海发布”微信号等报道，浦东机场昨晚（22日）连夜组织所有相关人员进行集体核酸检测。</p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1-wrapper" class="dfp-tag-wrapper">
<div id="dfp-ad-imu1" class="dfp-tag-wrapper">
      
</div>
</div></section>

<p>专业检测人员在浦东机场P4长时停车场二楼，设置了临时检测区域，现场对人员进行有序采样。</p>

